No, not really.

35
00:02:09,897 --> 00:02:12,126
I just like the movement of your eyes when you see colors.

36
00:02:16,237 --> 00:02:17,297
Let's make a deal.

37
00:02:17,836 --> 00:02:19,707
I'll teach you the colors of this world.

38
00:02:19,707 --> 00:02:22,806
