55
00:03:10,487 --> 00:03:12,586
Then to those standing beside and behind him, he went,

56
00:03:13,357 --> 00:03:14,757
"Don't you stare at that tree..."

57
00:03:15,526 --> 00:03:16,827
"and don't you get on the back of that bike."

58
